        "content": "The ID.4 comes with an 8-year or 100,000-mile high voltage battery warranty, providing peace of mind regarding battery performance and longevity. This warranty helps ensure that your vehicle's battery is covered for an extended period, allowing you to enjoy your electric driving experience with confidence.",
