        "content": "For the Volkswagen ID.4, charging from 10% to 80% can take as little as 28 minutes when using a high-speed DC charger. If charging at home with an 11 kW AC charger, it generally takes about 7.5 hours to charge from 0% to 100%. Please note that actual charging times may differ based on various factors, including battery conditions and the specific charging infrastructure used.",
